Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:31.93,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\an7\fs60\fax0.3\bord0\c&H545353&\pos(82,328.668)\frz339.2}跟钢人七濑有关系?
